				Jay and Mani Bhoola were with star of the night Xiuyan Li, right, at the Nelson Mandela Bay Table Tennis Union Awards evening last Friday at the Malabar Community Centre. Li led with seven awards
				
			
				
			
				
				Richard Pearse from the Chipembere Rhino Foundation, left, Craig Mittens from Barney’s Tarven and One Land’s Wayne Bolton celebrated a handover of  R26625 collected in aid of the foundation at a charity golf day held at the Humewood Golf Club Picture: Fredelin Adriaan
				
		



